<h1>说</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">shuō</span><span class=alesi>(shuo1)</span> , <span style="color:#000099;">shuì</span><span class=alesi>(shui4)</span> , <span style="color:#000099;">yuè</span><span class=alesi>(yue4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 说 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 说</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/speak" style="color:black;">speak</a>, <a href="/dictionary/say" style="color:black;">say</a>, <a href="/dictionary/talk" style="color:black;">talk</a>; scold, upbraid</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 9<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 9 strokes: <a href="/character/是" title="shi4: indeed, yes, right; to be; demonstrative pronoun, this, that">是</a>, <a href="/character/要" title="yao4: necessary, essential; necessity">要</a>, <a href="/character/种" title="zhong3: seed; race, breed; to plant">种</a>, <a href="/character/面" title="mian4: face; surface; plane; side, dimension">面</a>, <a href="/character/看" title="kan4: look, see; examine, scrutinize">看</a>, <a href="/character/前" title="qian2: in front, forward; preceding">前</a>, <a href="/character/点" title="dian3: dot, speck, spot; point, degree">点</a>, <a href="/character/将" title="jiang1: will, going to, future; general">将</a>, <a href="/character/很" title="hen3: very, quite, much">很</a>, <a href="/character/重" title="zhong4: heavy, weighty; double">重</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/言" title="Kangxi radical 149">言</a>&nbsp;149.7</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 1 <br><small>Other HSK 1 characters: <a href="/character/时" title="shi2: time, season; era, age, period">时</a>, <a href="/character/出" title="chu1: go out, send out; stand; produce">出</a>, <a href="/character/国" title="guo2: nation, country, nation-state">国</a>, <a href="/character/会" title="hui4: assemble, meet together; meeting">会</a>, <a href="/character/和" title="he2: harmony, peace; peaceful, calm">和</a>, <a href="/character/大" title="da4: big, great, vast, large, high">大</a>, <a href="/character/上" title="shang4: top; superior, highest; go up, send up">上</a>, <a href="/character/你" title="ni3: you, second person pronoun">你</a>, <a href="/character/对" title="dui4: correct, right; facing, opposed">对</a>, <a href="/character/来" title="lai2: come, coming; return, returning">来</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-1" title="List of HSK 1 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 1 charaters &raquo;</a></small></p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 24</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 1717</p><p><b>Traditional variant:</b> <a href="/character/說">說</a></p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/一说" title="yi1 shuo1">一说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/且说" title="qie3 shuo1">且说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/乱说" title="luan4 shuo1">乱说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/来说" title="lai2 shuo1">来说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/假说" title="jia3 shuo1">假说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/傅说" title="Fu4 Shuo1">傅说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/传说" title="chuan2 shuo1">传说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/再说" title="zai4 shuo1">再说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/分说" title="fen1 shuo1">分说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/剿说" title="chao1 shuo1">剿说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/劝说" title="quan4 shuo1">劝说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/好说" title="hao3 shuo1">好说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/妄说" title="wang4 shuo1">妄说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/学说" title="xue2 shuo1">学说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/小说" title="xiao3 shuo1">小说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/愣说" title="leng4 shuo1">愣说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/慢说" title="man4 shuo1">慢说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/成说" title="cheng2 shuo1">成说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/戏说" title="xi4 shuo1">戏说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/按说" title="an4 shuo1">按说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/推说" title="tui1 shuo1">推说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/据说" title="ju4 shuo1">据说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/浅说" title="qian3 shuo1">浅说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/演说" title="yan3 shuo1">演说</a>, <a href="/dictionary/漫说" title="man4 shuo1">漫说</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">說|说[<span style="color:#000099;">shuì</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- to persuade<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">說|说[<span style="color:#990000;">shuō</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- to speak<br>- to say<br>- to explain<br>- to scold<br>- to tell off<br>- a theory (usually in compounds such as <a href="/dictionary/日心说">日心说</a> heliocentric theory)<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+8BF4</p></div>

